OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother dry and bright day with
OL,6,Flong periods of sunshine. A chilly
OL,7,Fstart then becoming quite warm inland
OL,8,Fby the afternoon but cooler along the
OL,9,Fcoast with patchy mist in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some evening
OL,12,Fsunshine to start with, leading to
OL,13,Fclear spells. Patchy fog or frost may
OL,14,Fdevelop inland overnight, while low
OL,15,Fcloud and mist gradually return to the
OL,16,Fcoast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FAny overnight mist or fog
OL,19,Flifting through the morning but
OL,20,Fstaying dry and rather cloudy. A much
OL,21,Fcooler day than Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
